milestones.description: Bas Zuiderent and Eric's 67-run partnership is NED's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 66 between Bas Zuiderent and Reekers
Ashish Bagai and Sandeep Jyoti's 64-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 37 between John Davison and Ian Billcliff
Chumney and Don Maxwell's 95-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Ian Billcliff and Codrington
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (18) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for CAN, going past John Davison
